title: Fully Exposed, the "Full Frontal" Podcast With "All Time Low's" Alex Gaskarth & Jack Barakat Hits the Road This Week With a Live Podcast Tour
text:

SOURCE Sideshow Network
LOS ANGELES , Oct. 14, 2015 /PRNewswire/ -- With episode titles like Lord of the Ringworm, Dad Fro, Choose Your Own Hole, Guybrator and Bear Hospital, you know you can expect the unexpected from the podcast created by half of the band "All Time Low" with hosts (Singer) Alex Gaskarth and (Guitarist) Jack Barakat . "Full Frontal" is a program about music, pop-culture, TV and movies with a raw, no filter format. "Full Frontal" celebrity and music guests have included actress Abigail Breslin , Mark Hoppus of Blink-182, comedian Jonathan Kite of 2 BROKE GIRLS and early 2000's icon Tom Green . Starting this week fans will also have an opportunity to see Alex & Jack's "Full Frontal" Podcast up close and personal as they begin their live podcast tour October 16th at the Houston, TX Improv.
Logo - http://photos.prnewswire.com/prnh/20151014/276821LOGO
"Full Frontal" episodes can be heard every Monday at http://sideshownetwork.tv/fullfrontal
Live shows onsale now in the following cities with more dates to be announced:
Oct 16 – Houston, TX (Houston Improv) 1:00pm
Oct 17 – Addison ( Dallas ), TX (Addison Improv) 1:00pm
Oct 20 – Tempe, AZ (Tempe Improv) 1:00pm
Oct 22 – Los Angeles, CA (Hollywood Improv ) 8:00pm
Nov 23 – New York, NY (Gotham) 5:30pm
Seating is limited and tickets can be purchased at www.improv.com
Live show attendees under 18, must be accompanied by a parent or guardian.
